You are an expert in ontology engineering and Semantic Web standards.

Your task is to refine and align an existing OWL ontology with established ontologies, while preserving its conceptual structure.

Input

You will receive an OWL ontology in Turtle format that models the EU AI Act.

Goal

Improve the ontology by reusing existing ontologies where appropriate, specifically:

PROV-O (W3C Provenance Ontology)

ORG (W3C Organization Ontology)

The objective is to increase interoperability and semantic alignment without changing the original domain model.
